Air Date: 23 Mar 2014

Summary: Henry Myers (Drew Walters) is living a hard life, surviving on the frontier any way he can Ã¢â‚¬â€œ even if it means robbing a bank. After his latest heist backfires and his partners (Bea Smith and Rio Alexander) betray him and leave him for dead, Henry's life takes a surprising turn when he finds kindness and compassion from a widow (Erin Bethea) and her children (Jaden Roberts and Ezra Proch). 

 With this family's influence and support, Henry begins to question the choices he's made in his life. Just as things begin to make sense, Henry's life is shaken again when his old partners show up. Will Henry Myers seek the revenge he desires or finally find his redemption?
